              "number": 4,
              "headingEn": "4. What it means now + future influence + sensible qualification (Present → Future)",
              "headingZh": "",
              "textEn": "Even now, I can still hear her voice in the back of my mind whenever I feel self-doubt creeping in. Her influence has been long-lasting because it shaped the way I see learning, confidence, and even character. In the future, I hope I can pass that on to other people as well, especially if I ever mentor younger students or work in a leadership role. Of course, I do not think anyone should copy another person completely, because everyone has to find their own path. Even so, Mrs. Chan gave me a nudge in the right direction, and that made all the difference.",
              "textZh": "（直到現在，每當我開始懷疑自己時，我仍然好像會聽到她的聲音在我腦海裡出現。她的影響之所以這麼持久，是因為她改變了我看待學習、自信，甚至品格的方式。將來，我也希望自己可以把這份影響傳遞給其他人，尤其是如果我有一天要指導較年輕的學生，或者擔任帶領別人的角色。當然，我並不認為一個人應該完全複製另一個人，因為每個人都必須找到自己的路。即使如此，陳老師確實在關鍵時刻把我輕輕推向了正確的方向，而那已經帶來了很大的不同。）"
