              "textEn": "At present, I still run into him from time to time, and every conversation leaves me with something to reflect on. Even after a short chat, I often walk away feeling lighter and more awake. In the future, I hope I can stay as curious as he is, because he has shown me that an interesting person is not necessarily someone with a glamorous life. Sometimes it is simply someone who pays deep attention, tells stories well, and makes other people see the world with new eyes. That is exactly why I think he is such an interesting person.",
