            "raw": "Question: A person who loves to grow plants\nDescribe a person you know who loves to grow plants (vegetables, fruits,\nflowers).\n（題目：一位你認識、很喜歡種植物的人）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\n● who this person is\n（這個人是誰）\n● what they grow\n（他／她種甚麼）\n● where they grow them\n（他／她在哪裡種植）\n● explain why they enjoy growing plants\n（解釋為甚麼他／她喜歡種植物）\nPPF idea for this topic\nTalk about how this person became interested in growing plants in the past, what\nthey grow now in the present, and what they hope to grow or keep doing in the\nfuture. That way, your answer stays focused on one person but still gives you enough\nideas to speak for over 2 minutes.\n（PPF 小提示：你可以先講這個人過去是怎樣開始喜歡種植物的，再講他／她\n現在種些甚麼、在哪裡種，最後講他／她未來還想種甚麼或繼續怎樣做。這\n樣答案會一直圍繞同一個人，但仍然足夠你講超過兩分鐘。）"
