              "textEn": "I think she enjoys growing plants for several reasons. First of all, it helps her unwind. She has a busy job, and gardening gives her a chance to slow down and breathe. For her, it is more than a hobby; it is a form of quiet therapy. She once told me that when life feels noisy, plants bring her back to earth. I think that is a beautiful way to put it. She also loves the sense of reward that comes with it. Watching tiny seeds turn into something alive and healthy makes her feel that patience really pays off.",
              "textZh": "（我認為她喜歡種植物有幾個原因。首先，這能幫助她放鬆。她的工作很忙，而園藝給了她一個慢下來、喘一口氣的機會。對她來說，這不只是一個興趣，更像是一種安靜的療癒。她曾經跟我說，當生活太嘈雜的時候，植物會讓她重新腳踏實地。我覺得這說法很美。她也很喜歡那種有所收穫的感覺。看著小小的種子慢慢長成健康、有生命力的植物，會讓她覺得耐性終究是有回報的。）"
