            "raw": "Question: A Present or Gift You Have Given Someone\nDescribe a present or gift you have given someone.\n（題目：你送過別人的一份禮物）\nYou should say:\nWho you gave it to\n（你把禮物送給了誰）\nWhat kind of present it was\n（那是一份甚麼類型的禮物）\nHow it compared to other presents you have given\n（它跟你送過的其他禮物相比如何）\nExplain why you decided to give this particular gift.\n（解釋你為甚麼決定送這一份特別的禮物）\nPPF idea: keep one main gift, talk about when and why you gave it in the past, what it means now in the present, and how it may influence the way you choose gifts in future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中說一份主要禮物，先講你過去是在甚麼情況下送出的，再講這份禮物現在有甚麼意義，最後講它將來可能如何影響你送禮的方式。）"
