            "raw": "Question: A Present or Gift You Really Liked\n（題目：一份你很喜歡的禮物）\nDescribe a present or gift someone gave you that you really liked.\n（描述一份別人送給你、而你非常喜歡的禮物。）\n● You should say:\n（你應該說明：）\n● What kind of present it was\n（那是一份甚麼禮物）\n● Who gave it to you\n（是誰送給你的）\n● Why you were given it\n（你為甚麼會收到這份禮物）\n● Explain why you liked it\n（解釋你為甚麼喜歡它）\nPPF idea: keep one main gift, talk about when you received it in the past, how it fits into your life now in the present, and why you think you will still value it in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中講同一份禮物，先講你過去甚麼時候收到它，再講它現在如何融入你的生活，最後講你為甚麼覺得自己將來仍然會珍惜它。）"
