            "raw": "Question: Animal\n(題目：動物)\nDescribe an interesting animal you have seen.\n(描述一種你曾經見過的有趣動物。)\n● You should say:\n(你應該說明：)\n● What animal it was\n(那是甚麼動物)\n● When and where you saw it\n(你在甚麼時候、甚麼地方看見它)\n● And explain how you feel about this animal\n(並解釋你對這種動物有甚麼感受)\n● And explain why you think this animal is interesting.\n(並解釋你為甚麼覺得這種動物很有趣。)\nPPF idea: Past — when and where you saw the animal; Present — how you feel about it now; Future — whether you would like to see it again or learn more about it.\n(PPF 小提示：可以用過去、現在、未來去延伸同一種動物，例如你當時在哪裡看到牠、你現在對牠有甚麼感受，以及你將來是否還想再看見牠或了解更多。)"
