              "textEn": "I think sea turtles are interesting because they are both fragile and resilient at the same time. They seem peaceful, but they also survive long journeys and harsh natural conditions. That contrast makes them memorable to me. Looking back, that experience was more than just spotting an animal on a trip. It reminded me that nature does not need to be loud to be powerful. If I ever get the chance, I would love to see a sea turtle again, this time in the wild and for a little longer.",
              "textZh": "(我覺得海龜很有趣，因為牠們同時帶有脆弱和堅韌這兩種特質。牠們看起來很平和，但同時又能夠在漫長的旅程和嚴苛的自然環境中生存下來。這種反差令牠們特別令我難忘。如今回頭看，那次經歷已經不只是一次旅行中偶然看見動物那麼簡單。它提醒了我，大自然不需要很喧鬧，也可以很有力量。如果將來我有機會的話，我很想再看一次海龜，而且希望下一次是在真正的野外，並且能看久一點。)"
