            "raw": "Question: Books\nTalk about a book you are reading now or have read recently.\n（題目：書籍）\nYou should say:\nHow and why you got it\n（你是如何得到這本書，以及為甚麼會得到它）\nHow long it took you to read it, or how long you have been reading it\n（你花了多久讀完它，或者你已經讀了多久）\nWhat kind of book it is\n（它是一本甚麼類型的書）\nAnd say if you would like to read something else similar or not, and why\n（並說明你是否想再讀一些類似的書，以及原因）\nPPF idea: keep one main book, talk about how you got it and read it in the past, what effect it has on you now, and whether it makes you want to read similar books in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中說一本主要的書，先講你過去如何得到它和閱讀它，再講它現在對你有甚麼影響，以及它將來會不會令你想讀更多類似的書。）"
