              "textEn": "Yes, I definitely would. I would love to read more books in a similar style, especially novels that tell an engaging story while also leaving you with something deeper to think about. For me, the best books are not just page-turners; they leave an echo behind. Having said that, I would not want to read only this kind of book all the time, because if every story is too reflective, it can start to feel a bit heavy. Still, as an occasional read, this kind of novel is right up my alley. Overall, I am very glad I read it, because it was not only entertaining but also quietly meaningful, and it made me want to explore more fiction with the same emotional depth.",
              "textZh": "（會，我一定會。我很想再讀更多類似風格的書，尤其是那些一方面有吸引力的故事性，另一方面又能讓人留下更深思考的小說。對我來說，最好的書不只是讓人一直想翻頁的書；它們還會在你心裡留下回音。不過，話說回來，我也不會想一直只讀這一類書，因為如果每一本都太偏向反思，有時候也會開始讓人覺得有點沉重。即便如此，作為偶爾閱讀的一種選擇，這類小說真的很合我口味。總結來說，我很高興自己讀了這本書，因為它不但有趣，也帶著一種安靜而深刻的意義，而且它令我更想去探索那些同樣具有情感深度的小說。）"
