            "raw": "Question: Buildings\n（題目：建築物）\nDescribe a building that you particularly like.\n（描述一棟你特別喜歡的建築物。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nWhere the building is\n（那棟建築物在哪裡）\nWhat it looks like\n（它看起來是怎樣的）\nWhat you can do there\n（你可以在那裡做甚麼）\nExplain why you like this building.\n（解釋你為甚麼喜歡這棟建築物。）\nPPF idea: keep one building as your main focus. Talk about when you first knew it in the past, what it is like and what you do there now in the present, and why you may keep returning to it in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中講同一棟建築物。先講你過去是怎樣認識它的，再講它現在的樣子和你會在那裡做甚麼，最後帶到你將來為甚麼還會想再去。）"
