              "headingZh": "",
              "textEn": "The main reason I like this building is that it combines function with feeling. It is useful in a very practical sense, but at the same time it carries personal meaning for me. It reminds me of a period in my life when I was trying to become more disciplined and independent. Even now, it helps me clear my head and regain my focus. In the future, I think I will keep going back there whenever I need peace, perspective, or simply a break from the pace of daily life. So, although it may not be the most iconic building in Hong Kong, it is one that has quietly shaped me, and that is why it stands out so strongly in my mind.",
              "textZh": "（我喜歡這棟建築物的主要原因，是它把功能性和情感連結結合在一起。它在很實際的層面上十分有用，但同時對我來說又有很個人的意義。它會令我想起人生中一段努力讓自己變得更自律、更獨立的時期。直到現在，它仍然能幫助我整理思緒，重新集中精神。將來，我想我仍然會一直回到那裡，因為每當我需要平靜、需要重新看清事情，或者只是想暫時逃離日常生活的節奏時，那裡都很適合。所以，雖然它未必是香港最具代表性的建築物，但它是一棟默默塑造過我的建築物，而這正是它一直深深留在我心裡的原因。）"
