            "raw": "Question: Change\nDescribe a positive change in your life.\n（題目：你人生中的一個正面改變）\n● You should say:\n（你應該說明：）\n● what the change was about\n（這個改變是關於甚麼的）\n● when it happened\n（它是在甚麼時候發生的）\n● describe details of the change that happened\n（描述這個改變的具體情況）\n● and describe how it affected you later in life\n（並描述它後來如何影響你的人生）\nPPF idea for this topic Use one clear life change and extend it through Past, Present, Future. ● Past: what your life was like before the change, and when it happened ● Present: what changed in your habits, mindset, or daily routine ● Future: how this change may continue to shape your life\n（PPF 小提示：集中講一個清楚的人生改變，然後用過去、現在、未來去自然延伸。過去講改變發生前你的狀態，以及它在甚麼時候出現；現在講你的習慣、心態或生活節奏有甚麼改變；未來講這個改變會如何繼續影響你。）"
