            "raw": "Question: A Uniform You Have Worn\n（題目：你曾經穿過的一套制服）\nDescribe a uniform you have worn (such as a school or company uniform).\n（描述一套你曾經穿過的制服，例如校服或公司制服。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\n● what it looked like\n（它看起來是怎樣的）\n● when and where you needed to wear this uniform\n（你在甚麼時候、甚麼地方需要穿這套制服）\n● who paid for this uniform\n（這套制服是由誰付錢買的）\n● and explain how you felt about that uniform\n（並解釋你對這套制服有甚麼感受）\nPPF idea: keep one main uniform, talk about what it was like in the past, how you feel about it now in the present, and what it still represents to you in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中講一套制服，先講它在過去是怎樣的，再講你現在對它的感受，最後講它在未來對你來說仍然代表甚麼。）"
