            "raw": "Question: City\n（題目：城市）\nDescribe your favourite city or a city you have visited that you like very much.\n（描述你最喜歡的城市，或者一個你去過而且非常喜歡的城市。）\n● You should say:\n（你應該說明：）\n● What is its name and where it is\n（它叫甚麼名字，以及它位於哪裡）\n● when you visited it\n（你是在甚麼時候去的）\n● why you liked it\n（你為甚麼喜歡它）\n● And the major attractions in this city are\n（以及這個城市的主要景點是甚麼）\nPPF idea: keep one main city as the focus, talk about when you visited it in the past, why it still stays in your mind in the present, and whether you would like to go back in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中講一個主要城市，先講你過去甚麼時候去過，再講它現在為何仍然留在你心裡，最後再講你將來會不會想再去。）"
