              "textEn": "I would definitely like to visit Kyoto again in the future, perhaps in autumn next time, because I have heard that the red and orange leaves make the city even more breathtaking. I think it is the kind of place that reveals something new every time you go back. Overall, Kyoto left a deep impression on me because it was beautiful without being superficial, and cultural without feeling distant. It was like reading a quiet but unforgettable novel.",
              "textZh": "（我將來一定會想再去一次京都，也許下次會選擇秋天，因為我聽說當紅葉和橙葉出現的時候，整個城市會更加令人驚嘆。我覺得京都就是那種每次重遊，都會展現出新一面的地方。總結來說，京都給我留下了非常深刻的印象，因為它美得不流於表面，而且很有文化氣息，卻不會讓人感到遙遠。它就像一本安靜但令人難忘的小說。）"
