              "textEn": "One company that I know quite well is a medium-sized education technology company called BrightPath Learning. I first heard about it through a close friend, who joined it two years ago as a content designer. Since then, I have learned quite a lot about how it works, what kind of people work there, and what its culture is like. So, although I have never worked there, I still feel I know it fairly well.",
