              "textEn": "As for the working environment, I would say that seems to be one of its biggest strengths. My friend has told me that the office is modern and comfortable, but more importantly, the atmosphere is supportive rather than tense. People are encouraged to share ideas, and managers seem approachable instead of distant. What I particularly like is that junior staff are not treated as if they are invisible. Their opinions are taken seriously. Of course, there are deadlines and pressure, but people seem to solve problems together rather than blame one another.",
              "textZh": "（至於那裡的工作環境，我會說這似乎是它其中一個最大的優點。我的朋友告訴我，那裡的辦公室很現代，也很舒適，但更重要的是，整體氣氛是支持性的，而不是緊張壓迫的。人們會被鼓勵分享想法，而管理層也給人一種平易近人的感覺，而不是高高在上。我特別欣賞的一點是，初級員工不會被當成透明人一樣對待。他們的意見是會被認真看待的。當然，那裡仍然有截止日期和工作壓力，不過人們似乎會一起解決問題，而不是互相推卸責任。）"
