            "raw": "Question: Environment\nDescribe an environmental problem or event.\n（題目：描述一個環境問題或事件）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\n● What it is\n（它是甚麼）\n● Where it is happening\n（它在哪裡發生）\n● What problems it causes\n（它造成了甚麼問題）\n● And what you think will happen in the future regarding this event\n（以及你認為這個事件未來會怎樣發展）\nPPF idea: keep one environmental problem and extend it clearly PPF 小提示：集中講一個環境問題，然後自然地用過去、現在、未來去延伸 ● Past: when you first became aware of it （過去：你是甚麼時候開始留意到這個問題的） ● Present: what it is, where it is happening, and what damage it causes （現在：它是甚麼、在哪裡發生，以及它造成甚麼破壞） ● Future: what may happen if people ignore it, or what may improve if action is taken （未來：如果人們忽視它會怎樣，或者如果採取行動情況會怎樣改善）"
