              "headingEn": "2. What happened (Past)",
              "headingZh": "（2. 當時發生了甚麼（過去））",
              "textEn": "At first, I found it hard to stay calm. My breathing felt awkward, and for a moment I honestly thought about backing out. However, the instructor was very patient and kept telling me to slow down and trust the process. Once we went below the surface, everything changed. The noise of the outside world disappeared, and it felt as if I had entered a completely different world. The water was crystal clear, small silver fish swam around us, and sunlight shimmered on the rocks below. It was like stepping into a living postcard.",
              "textZh": "（起初，我很難令自己保持冷靜。我的呼吸感覺很不自然，而有一刻我真的想過放棄。不過，教練非常有耐性，一直叫我要慢下來，相信整個過程。當我們真的潛到水面以下時，一切都改變了。外面世界的聲音消失了，感覺就像我走進了一個完全不同的世界。海水清澈見底，銀色的小魚在我們身邊游來游去，陽光在下方的岩石上閃閃發亮。那感覺就像走進了一張活生生的明信片。）"
