              "textEn": "What made the experience especially exciting was the mixture of fear, beauty, and novelty. On the one hand, I was completely out of my comfort zone, so every second felt intense and unforgettable. On the other hand, the underwater scenery was so calm and beautiful that I forgot my fear for a while. That contrast made the experience much more powerful. It was not just enjoyable; it made me feel fully awake and completely present in the moment.",
              "textZh": "（這次經歷之所以特別令人興奮，是因為它同時結合了恐懼、美感和新鮮感。一方面，我完全走出了自己的舒適圈，所以每一秒都顯得特別強烈，也特別難忘。另一方面，海底的景色又是那麼平靜、那麼美麗，令我暫時忘記了自己的害怕。正是這種對比，令整個經歷變得更加有力量。它不只是令人開心，而是讓我感到自己在那一刻完全清醒、完全投入。）"
