            "raw": "Question: Health Article\n（題目：健康文章）\nDescribe an article you read in a magazine or on the Internet that could help people improve their health.\n（描述一篇你在雜誌或網上讀過、能幫助人們改善健康的文章。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nwhen you read it\n（你是在甚麼時候讀到它的）\nwhere you read it\n（你在哪裡讀到它的）\nwhat it was about\n（它是關於甚麼的）\nand explain why (you think) it could improve people’s health.\n（並解釋為甚麼你認為它能改善人們的健康。）\nPPF idea: keep one main article as the focus, talk about when and where you read it in the past, why it matters now in the present, and how its advice could help people in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中講一篇主要文章，先講你過去是在甚麼時候、哪裡讀到它，再講它現在為何有意義，最後再講它的建議將來如何幫助人們。）"
