              "textEn": "One historical place I have visited is the Forbidden City in Beijing. It is an enormous imperial palace complex right in the centre of the city, and I went there a few years ago during a family trip to mainland China. Before that visit, I had seen it only in textbooks and documentaries, so seeing it with my own eyes felt a bit surreal.",
