              "textEn": "One occasion I remember clearly was when I forgot to bring my passport on a short trip to Macau with my family last year. We had already left home early in the morning and were halfway to the ferry terminal when I suddenly checked my bag and realized it was not there. My heart absolutely sank. I had packed clothes, my charger, and even snacks for the journey, but I had somehow left the one document I could not travel without on my desk at home.",
