            "raw": "Question: A Happy Childhood Event\n（題目：一件快樂的童年往事）\nDescribe a happy childhood event.\n（描述一件快樂的童年往事。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nWhen it happened\n（它是在甚麼時候發生的）\nWho was involved\n（有誰參與）\nHow you felt at the time\n（你當時有甚麼感受）\nExplain why you remember this particular occasion.\n（解釋你為甚麼特別記得這次事情。）\nPPF idea: keep one main occasion, talk about what happened then in the past, how you feel about it now in the present, and why you think it will stay with you in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中講一個主要場合，先講它在過去是怎樣發生的，再講你現在對它有甚麼感受，最後講你為甚麼覺得它將來仍然會留在你的記憶裡。）"
