              "textEn": "I still remember this occasion so clearly because it captures something very pure about childhood. It reminds me of a time when happiness was simple, immediate, and wholehearted. Even now, when I think about that day, I can almost hear the laughter and feel the spring breeze again. Overall, I remember it because it was not just a birthday celebration; it was a small moment of love that stayed with me and still brightens my memory today more than presents ever did.",
              "textZh": "（我之所以到現在仍然這麼清楚記得這次事情，是因為它抓住了童年裡某種非常純粹的東西。它讓我想起一段快樂很簡單、很直接，而且很真心的時光。即使到了現在，每當我想起那一天，我幾乎仍然能聽到笑聲，也仍然能感受到春天的微風。總結來說，我會記得它，不只是因為那是一場生日慶祝，而是因為那是一個小小卻充滿愛的時刻；它一直留在我心裡，直到今天，帶給我的光亮甚至比禮物本身還要多。）"
