            "raw": "Question: Money\n（題目：金錢）\nDescribe what you would do if you received a very large amount of money.\n（描述如果你收到一大筆錢，你會做甚麼。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nwho you would share it with\n（你會和誰分享）\nwhat you would buy\n（你會買甚麼）\nwhat else you would do\n（你還會做甚麼）\nand explain how you would feel about getting so much money.\n（並解釋如果得到這麼多錢，你會有甚麼感受。）\nPPF idea: keep one main imagined situation. Talk about why your priorities come from past experiences, what you would choose now, and how this money would affect your future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中講一個主要的想像情境。先講你的優先次序如何來自過去的經歷，再講你現在會怎樣選擇，最後帶到這筆錢會如何影響你的未來。）"
