              "textEn": "If I received a lot of money, I would share it with my family, especially my parents. They have supported me for years, so helping them would feel right. I would want to reduce their pressure and make life easier. In the past, I often saw them work hard and worry about expenses. That is why my first instinct would not be to show off. It would be to give something back to the people who have stood by me.",
              "textZh": "（如果我收到一大筆錢，我會和家人分享，尤其是我的父母。他們多年來一直支持我，所以先幫助他們會讓我覺得很應該。我會想減輕他們的壓力，讓生活變得更輕鬆。過去，我經常看到他們辛苦工作，也為開支而擔心。正因如此，我第一個反應不會是炫耀，而是回饋那些一直站在我身邊的人。）"
