            "raw": "Question: Favourite Song\n（題目：最喜歡的歌曲）\nDescribe your favourite song.\n（描述你最喜歡的一首歌。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nWhat is the name of the song\n（那首歌叫甚麼名字）\nWhat the song is about\n（那首歌是關於甚麼的）\nWhen you first heard the song\n（你最初是甚麼時候聽到這首歌的）\nExplain why it is your favourite song.\n（解釋為甚麼它是你最喜歡的歌曲。）\nPPF idea: Past — when you first heard the song; Present — what the song is about and what it means to you now; Future — why it may remain your favourite for years.\n（PPF 小提示：過去可講你最初是何時聽到這首歌；現在可講它的內容和它現在對你的意義；未來則可講它為甚麼多年後仍可能是你的最愛。）"
