              "textEn": "One of my favourite songs is Fix You by Coldplay. It is quite an old song now, but for me it has never lost its emotional power. I first heard it when I was in secondary school, probably around the time I was preparing for an important exam. A classmate played it during a break, and the melody caught my attention immediately. It sounded gentle at first, almost fragile, but there was also something quietly powerful about it.",
              "textZh": "（我最喜歡的其中一首歌是 Coldplay 的《Fix You》。這首歌現在已經算是比較舊的歌了，但對我來說，它從來沒有失去那種情感力量。我第一次聽到它，是在我讀中學的時候，大概正值我準備一場重要考試的那段日子。一位同學在小息時播放了這首歌，而它的旋律立刻吸引了我的注意。它一開始聽起來很溫柔，甚至有點脆弱，但同時又帶著一種安靜而有力的感覺。）"
