              "textEn": "An interesting piece of news I recently read was about university students who created a device to collect plastic waste from a polluted river. I came across the story about three weeks ago on a news app at night. At first, I nearly skipped it because it sounded like another environmental report. However, the more I read, the more it caught my attention, because it was not just about a problem. It was about a practical attempt to solve one.",
              "textZh": "（我最近讀到的一則有趣新聞，是關於一班大學生設計出一個裝置，用來收集受污染河流中的塑膠垃圾。我大約在三星期前的晚上，在一個新聞應用程式上看到這則報道。起初，我差點把它滑過，因為它聽起來像另一則普通的環保新聞。不過，我越讀越覺得它吸引，因為它不只是講一個問題，而是在講一個實際解決問題的嘗試。）"
