            "raw": "Question: Your Favourite Festival or Celebration\n（題目：你最喜歡的節日或慶祝活動）\nDescribe your favourite festival or celebration.\n（描述你最喜歡的節日或慶祝活動。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nWhat time of year it is\n（它是在一年中的甚麼時候）\nWhy you like it\n（你為甚麼喜歡它）\nWhat you usually do\n（你通常會做甚麼）\nAnd say how that festival or celebration compares to others in your country or abroad.\n（並說明這個節日或慶祝活動跟你國家內其他節日或外國節日相比如何。）\nPPF idea: keep one main festival, talk about how it felt in the past, what you usually do now in the present, and why you think it will remain special in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中講一個主要節日，先講它在過去帶給你甚麼感覺，再講你現在通常怎樣過，最後講你為甚麼覺得它在未來仍然會很特別。）"
