              "textEn": "The crowded place I would like to talk about was the Lunar New Year flower market I visited earlier this year in Victoria Park in Hong Kong. I went there in the evening, just a few days before the festival, with my cousin and my younger sister. We chose that time because the market is always at its liveliest after dark, when the lights are bright, the stalls are packed, and the whole place feels as if the city is humming.",
              "textZh": "（我想說的一個擠迫地方，是我今年早些時候去過的農曆新年年宵市場，地點在香港維多利亞公園。我是在晚上去的，當時距離新年只有幾天，而且我是和表哥以及妹妹一起去的。我們選擇那個時間，是因為市場在入夜後總是最熱鬧，燈光很亮，攤位擠滿了人，而整個地方都像是整座城市在嗡嗡作響。）"
