            "raw": "Question: Photograph\n(題目：照片)\nDescribe a photograph that you like.\n(描述一張你喜歡的照片。)\nYou should say:\n(你應該說明：)\nwho is in the photograph\n(照片裡有誰)\nwhen the photograph was taken\n(這張照片是在甚麼時候拍的)\nwhere the photograph is\n(這張照片現在在哪裡)\nand explain why you like the photograph.\n(並解釋你為甚麼喜歡這張照片。)\nPPF idea: keep one photograph as the focus, talk about when it was taken in the past, describe where it is and what it means to you now in the present, and explain why it may remain special to you in the future.\n(小提示：集中講同一張照片，先講它在過去是甚麼時候拍的，再講它現在放在哪裡、對你有甚麼意義，最後講它為甚麼在未來仍然會對你很特別。)"
