              "textEn": "That photograph was taken about five years ago during a family trip to Okinawa in Japan. We had spent the whole day visiting shops, eating seafood, and walking along the coast, so by evening everyone was tired but happy. Just before we left the beach, my father asked a passerby to take one quick photo for us. None of us expected it to turn out so well, which is probably part of the reason it feels so genuine and unforced.",
              "textZh": "(這張照片大約是在五年前拍的，當時我們一家人去了日本沖繩旅行。我們那天整天都在逛商店、吃海鮮，還沿著海邊散步，所以到了傍晚，大家都累了，但心情很好。就在我們準備離開沙灘之前，我爸爸請一位路人幫我們快速拍了一張照片。當時沒有一個人想到它最後會拍得這麼好，而我想這大概也是它讓人感到如此真實自然的原因之一。)"
