            "raw": "Question: Products\n（題目：產品）\nDescribe something which is produced in your country, such as food, a handicraft, or a car.\n（描述一樣在你的國家生產的東西，例如食物、手工藝品，或者汽車。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nWhat it is\n（它是甚麼）\nWhat it is used for\n（它是用來做甚麼的）\nHow it is made or produced\n（它是怎樣製作或生產的）\nAnd explain why your country produces this thing\n（並解釋為甚麼你的國家會生產這種東西）\nPPF idea: Past — when you first became aware of this product; Present — what it is, what it is used for, and how it is made; Future — why it may remain important or famous.\n（PPF 小提示：過去可講你甚麼時候開始留意這種產品；現在可講它是甚麼、用來做甚麼，以及怎樣製作；未來則可講它為甚麼可能會繼續重要或出名。）"
