              "headingEn": "4. Explain why this book is your favourite",
              "headingZh": "（4. 解釋為甚麼這本書是你最喜歡的）",
              "textEn": "This is why it remains my favourite book even now. It is short, but it contains far more feeling and insight than many longer novels. I can read it quickly, yet it stays in my mind for a long time, which is quite rare. I also love the fact that it is tender without being sentimental. If I had to recommend just one book to someone, I would probably choose this one, because it is simple, beautiful, and unforgettable.",
              "textZh": "（這就是為甚麼直到現在，它仍然是我最喜歡的一本書。它雖然很短，卻包含了比很多長篇小說更多的感情和洞見。我可以很快把它讀完，但它卻會在我心裡停留很久，而這其實是很難得的。我也很喜歡它那種溫柔而不煽情的特質。如果我要向別人推薦一本書，我大概會選這一本，因為它簡單、美麗，而且令人難忘。）"
