            "raw": "Question: A Website That You Visit a Lot\n（題目：一個你經常瀏覽的網站）\nDescribe a website that you visit a lot.\n（描述一個你經常瀏覽的網站。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nWhat the website is about\n（這個網站是關於甚麼的）\nHow you found the website\n（你是怎樣找到這個網站的）\nWho else you told about the website\n（你還把這個網站介紹給了誰）\nExplain why you visit the website a lot.\n（解釋你為甚麼經常瀏覽這個網站。）\nPPF idea: keep one main website, talk about how you found it in the past, how you use it now in the present, and whether you think you will keep using it in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中講一個主要網站，先講你過去是怎樣找到它的，再講你現在如何使用它，最後講你將來會不會繼續使用它。）"
