            "raw": "Question: Rules\n（題目：規則）\nDescribe a traffic rule or law you know about.\n（描述一條你知道的交通規則或法律。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nwhat it is\n（它是甚麼）\nhow you know about it\n（你是怎樣知道它的）\nif you follow this rule or law\n（你有沒有遵守這條規則或法律）\nand explain why this rule is important.\n（並解釋為甚麼這條規則很重要。）\nPPF idea: keep one main rule as your focus. Talk about how you first learned it in the past, whether you follow it now in the present, and why it will still matter in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中講一條主要規則。先講你過去如何認識它，再講你現在有沒有遵守它，最後帶到它在未來為甚麼仍然重要。）"
