            "raw": "Question: Describe a rule you had to obey when you were in school.\n(題目：描述一條你在學校時必須遵守的規則。)\nYou should say:\n(你應該說明：)\nwhat the rule was\n(那條規則是甚麼)\nif you agreed with the rule\n(你是否同意那條規則)\nwhy the rule existed\n(那條規則為甚麼存在)\nand what would happen if students broke the rule.\n(以及如果學生違反規則會發生甚麼事。)\nPPF idea: Past — what the rule was and how you felt about it then; Present — why you understand it better now; Future — what kind of rule you think schools will still need in the future.\n(PPF 小提示：過去可講那條規則是甚麼，以及你當時對它有甚麼感覺；現在可講你為甚麼現在更理解它；未來則可講你覺得學校將來仍然需要哪一類規則。)"
