            "raw": "Question: Future Study\n（題目：未來想學習的科目）\nTalk about a subject you would like to study in the future.\n（談談一個你將來想學習的科目。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nWhy you want to study that subject\n（你為甚麼想學那個科目）\nWhat things about that subject you find particularly interesting\n（那個科目有哪些地方令你特別感興趣）\nWhere it is possible to study that subject\n（在哪裡可以讀那個科目）\nAnd say if you think you will start studying it soon or not, and why\n（並說明你覺得自己會不會很快開始學，以及原因）\nPPF idea: Past — when you first became interested in the subject; Present — why it interests you and where you can study it; Future — whether you think you will start soon and why.\n（PPF 小提示：過去可講你何時開始對這個科目有興趣；現在可講你為甚麼喜歡它，以及可以在哪裡學；未來則可講你會不會很快開始學，以及原因。）"
