              "headingEn": "1. Opening: what the problem is",
              "headingZh": "(1. 開場：這個問題是甚麼)",
              "textEn": "One problem in my city that stands out immediately is the lack of affordable housing in Hong Kong. It is something people talk about constantly, whether they are students, young workers, or families with children. I became aware of it quite early, because even when I was in secondary school, adults around me were already discussing rent, waiting lists, and tiny flats. In a city full of wealth and modern buildings, that contrast can feel quite striking.",
              "textZh": "(我城市裡其中一個最明顯的問題，就是香港缺乏可負擔的住屋。無論是學生、年輕上班族，還是有孩子的家庭，大家都經常談到這件事。我很早就已經留意到這個問題，因為即使在我讀中學的時候，身邊的大人已經在談租金、輪候名單，以及狹小的單位。在一座充滿財富和現代建築的城市裡，這種反差其實相當強烈。)"
