            "raw": "Question: Sports\n（題目：運動）\nTalk about a sport you like doing or watching.\n（談談一項你喜歡做或喜歡觀看的運動。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nHow you first became interested in it\n（你最初是怎樣對它產生興趣的）\nWhy you are interested in it\n（你為甚麼對它有興趣）\nWhat equipment and skills are needed for it\n（這項運動需要甚麼裝備和技巧）\nAnd say if you think it is an easy sport to do or not, and why\n（並說明你覺得它是否容易進行，以及原因）\nPPF idea: Past — how you first became interested in the sport; Present — why it interests you and what equipment and skills it needs; Future — whether you think it is easy and why you may keep following it.\n（小提示：過去可講你何時開始對這項運動有興趣；現在可講你為甚麼喜歡它，以及它需要甚麼裝備和技巧；未來則可講你覺得它容不容易，以及你是否會繼續接觸它。）"
