              "textEn": "One sport I would really like to try is rock climbing, especially indoor rock climbing. I first became interested in it a couple of years ago after watching a short documentary about beginners learning how to climb. What caught my attention was the mix of strength, balance, and concentration. It did not seem like a sport that depended only on speed or power. Instead, it looked almost like solving a puzzle with your whole body, which made it seem both challenging and exciting to me.",
