            "raw": "Question: A Day Trip You Have Been On\n（題目：你去過的一次即日來回旅行）\nTalk about a day trip you have been on.\n（談談你曾經去過的一次即日來回旅行。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nWhere you went\n（你去了哪裡）\nHow you travelled\n（你是怎樣去的）\nWhy you chose to go to that place\n（你為甚麼選擇去那個地方）\nAnd say whether you would like to go back to the same place again or not, and why.\n（並說明你會不會想再去同一個地方，以及原因。）\nPPF idea: Past — where you went and how you got there; Present — why that trip still stands out to you; Future — whether you would like to return.\n（PPF 小提示：過去可講你去了哪裡以及如何到達；現在可講這次旅程為甚麼仍令你印象深刻；未來則可講你會不會想再去。）"
