              "headingZh": "（1. 你去了哪裡，以及你是怎樣去的）",
              "textEn": "One day trip I remember clearly was a visit to Cheung Chau, which is a small outlying island in Hong Kong. I went there last spring with two close friends on a Saturday when we all happened to be free. To get there, we took the MTR to Central and then caught a ferry. The journey itself was part of the fun because once the boat left the harbour the city noise faded and the day felt lighter and relaxed.",
              "textZh": "（我記得很清楚的一次即日來回旅行，是去長洲，那是香港一個小小的離島。我去年春天和兩位好朋友在一個大家剛好都有空的星期六去了那裡。為了去那裡，我們先坐港鐵去中環，然後再乘搭渡輪。旅程本身已經是樂趣的一部分，因為當船一離開海港，城市的嘈音就慢慢退去，而整天的感覺也變得更輕鬆、更放鬆。）"
