            "raw": "Question: A Job You Would Like to Do in the Future\n（題目：你將來想從事的一份工作）\nDescribe a job you would like to do in the future.\n（描述一份你將來想做的工作。）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\nHow and when you first became interested in that job\n（你最初是怎樣、以及在甚麼時候對那份工作產生興趣）\nWhat people in that job have to do every day\n（做那份工作的人每天要做甚麼）\nWhat qualifications and experience you need in order to get that job\n（你需要甚麼資歷和經驗才能得到那份工作）\nAnd say if you think you will be able to get that job or not, and why.\n（並說明你覺得自己能不能得到那份工作，以及原因。）\nPPF idea: keep one main job, talk about how it first attracted you in the past, what it involves now in the present, and whether you think you can reach it in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中講一份主要工作，先講它在過去是怎樣吸引你，再講它現在包括甚麼內容，最後講你覺得自己未來能否做到。）"
