              "textEn": "One piece of advice I recently received came from my manager about two months ago, after I had finished a presentation at work. We were discussing the project afterward in a meeting room, and although the presentation had gone reasonably well, I could tell she wanted to mention something important. She was supportive rather than critical, which made me listen even more carefully.",
              "textZh": "（我最近收到的一個建議，是兩個月前在我完成一個工作簡報之後，由我的經理給我的。當時，我們在會議室裡討論那個項目。雖然整個簡報算是進行得不錯，但我感覺得到她想提一件重要的事。她的態度比較像支持，而不是批評，所以我也聽得更加認真。）"
