              "headingZh": "（1. 開場：那是在甚麼時候，以及我和誰在一起）",
              "textEn": "One time I felt deeply embarrassed was during a school assembly in my final year of secondary school. It happened on a Friday morning, and the whole year level had gathered in the hall. I was there with my classmates, several teachers, and even the principal, which made the situation feel much bigger. At that point, I had no idea that within a few minutes I would become the centre of attention for completely the wrong reason. I remember everything.",
              "textZh": "（有一次我感到非常尷尬，是在我中學最後一年的一次學校集會上。事情發生在一個星期五早上，整個年級的人都聚集在禮堂裡。我當時和同學、幾位老師，甚至校長都在一起，所以整件事顯得特別大件。那時候，我完全不知道幾分鐘之後，我竟然會因為最錯誤的原因成為全場焦點。我到現在仍然記得很清楚。）"
