              "textEn": "One person I know who is genuinely kind is my aunt, Linda. She is my mother's older sister, so I have known her for my whole life, but I became especially close to her during my teenage years. At that time, I often visited her home after school because it was near my bus stop. Little by little, she became more than just a relative to me. She felt like someone I could always turn to without hesitation.",
              "textZh": "(我認識的一個真正很善良的人，是我的姨媽 Linda。她是我媽媽的姐姐，所以我一生下來就認識她，但我在青少年時期才跟她變得特別親近。那時候，我放學後經常會去她家，因為她家剛好在我巴士站附近。慢慢地，她對我來說已經不只是一位親戚。她更像是一個我可以毫不猶豫就去依靠的人。)"
