              "textEn": "I do not go there every week, but I visit it a few times a year, especially when the weather is mild. I tend to go there on weekends or public holidays, usually with one or two family members or sometimes with a close friend. I like that it never feels exactly the same. On sunny days it feels lively and bright, while on cooler evenings it becomes calmer and almost reflective, which gives it a different kind of charm.",
              "textZh": "（我不是每個星期都去，但我一年會去幾次，特別是在天氣比較溫和的時候。我通常會在週末或公眾假期去，多數是和一兩位家人一起，有時候也會和一位親近的朋友去。我喜歡它的一點，是它從來不會給人完全一樣的感覺。晴天的時候，它顯得很有活力，也很明亮；而天氣較涼的傍晚，它又會變得更平靜，甚至有一點沉思的感覺，而這正正給了它另一種魅力。）"
