              "textEn": "One article I remember clearly was about how a short daily walk could improve physical and mental health. I read it around six months ago, during a stressful period when I was spending too much time indoors. At that point, I was sleeping badly, sitting for long hours, and feeling tired for no obvious reason. The article caught my attention because it did not promise miracles. Instead, it focused on one simple habit that seemed realistic and powerful for ordinary people.",
